Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.64,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば髪をちょっとなびかせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.89,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聴こえる声{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.95,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　何と言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.90,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}足は止めませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.40,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}飛ぶ鳥落とす勢い　ニュース
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}明日には忘れている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}昨日よりも今日がいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}思い込み　大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}リズムに合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.33,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}揺れていたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}外野がうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:14.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ノイズ・キャンセリング
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.64,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば指をちょっとなぞらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君のチョイス{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.89,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　頬を赤くして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唾を吐きかけ{\fsp4}る{\fsp0}Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.47,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:41.51,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聽到的會是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 無論別人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.40,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新聞的傳播勢不可擋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神勝利大法好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟著節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}搖擺搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:14.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指轉個圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的選擇是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 憋紅了臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}準備唾棄的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:31.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}興趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但決定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:41.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}僅僅是喜歡還是討厭
